title: Kendall Jenner fuels dating rumor in Milan with A$AP Rocky
text:
The rumors have been swirling for months.
And Kendall Jenner , 21, continues to fuel the fire she is dating A$AP Rocky, 28, as they enjoyed another romantic evening out, this time in Milan, Italy .
The two were seen arriving at their hotel together in the Italian city on Tuesday with Kendall dressed down in leather pants and a dark green hooded jacket.
Scroll down for video
Are they a couple? Kendall Jenner, 21, continues to fuel the fire with another romantic evening out with A$AP Rocky, 28, after touching down in Milan, Italy
The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star wore her hair loose around her face and appeared to wear very little makeup as the duo stepped out of their car and into their hotel.
Known for being the most casual of the group, Kendall paired her tight leather pants with black pointed boots and a light colored graphic tee.
She held her phone and red patent leather wallet tightly to her chest as she walked the short distance outside in the Italian city.
A$AP Rocky complemented Kendall's look with a long brown overcoat that he paired with beige pants and white running shoes.
Casual chic: The two were seen arriving at their hotel together in the Italian city on Tuesday with Kendall dressed down in leather pants and a dark green hooded jacket
Love for fashion! A$ASP Rocky complemented Kendall's look with a long brown overcoat that he paired with beige pants and white running shoes
He kept his look casual by pairing the fancy jacket with big gold buttons with a basic grey hoodie.
Kendall's rapper beau carried a Fendi bag and accessorized with plenty of jewelry around his fingers, wrists and neck.
Romance rumours have been swirling regarding Kendall and A$AP for months - and they have been seen together a lot more recently.
Keeping it simple: Known for being the most casual of the group, Kendall paired her tight leather pants with black pointed boots and a light colored graphic tee
European tour: Kendall touched down in Milan, Italy after partying with some friends in London
Last month, the duo were seen browsing the shops of Paris after the rapper flew out to join her.
Neither has even confirmed if their dating with Kendall notoriously secretive about her relationships.
A$AP meanwhile was engaged to Chanel Iman but the couple split in 2014.
Casual traveler: She was spotted wearing leggings and black tennis shoes that she paired with a Fila sweatshirt
Kendall has been spotted out with the rapper on several occasions, with Us Weekly reporting in June that the pair were enjoying a 'fling.'
A source told the site: 'It's a fling. It's not serious.'
But the musician was said to very impressed with the sister of Kim, Khloe, Kourtney and Kylie, with the source adding: 'He thinks Kendall's hot as hell. He's just having fun.'
The site's insider claimed that Kendall and A$AP (real name Rakim Mayers) have bonded over their mutual love of fashion.
Is it a fling? Kendall has been spotted out with the rapper on several occasions, with Us Weekly reporting in June that the pair were enjoying a 'fling.' Pictured January in Paris
'They're both major players,' the publication's source said. 'They have lots to talk about!'
Kendall has also been linked to LA Lakers basketball player Jordan Clarkson, with a report emerging last month that the pair got 'touchy-feely' at Drake's party following the American Music Awards.
'You could see that they're really into each other and they certainly weren't hiding it,' the eyewitness told E! News. 'They were very touchy-feely!
'She was super giddy and loving every minute of it. It was obvious that they have a very playful, fun relationship,' the eyewitness added.
Cool and chic: She remained casual with her newly cut hair hanging down straight and parted in the center, while sporting large sunglasses
